<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٧]</span> وَقَوْلُ مُدْخِلٍ: <span class="c2">«بِاسْمِ اللهِ، وَعَلَى مِلَّةِ رَسُولِ اللهِ صلى الله عليه وسلم»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٨]</span> وَلَحْدُهُ عَلَى شِقِّهِ الأَيْمَنِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَيَجِبُ اسْتِقْبَالُهُ القِبْلَةَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَكُرِهَ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> بِلَا حَاجَةٍ جُلُوسُ تَابِعِهَا قَبْلَ وَضْعِهَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَتَجْصِيصُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> قَبْرٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَبِنَاءٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَكِتَابَةٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> وَمَشْيٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٦]</span> وَجُلُوسٌ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٧]</span> وَإِدْخَالُهُ شَيْئاً مَسَّتْهُ النَّارُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[٨]</span> وَتَبَسُّمٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[٩]</span> وَحَدِيثٌ بِأَمْرِ الدُّنْيَا عِنْدَهُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَحَرُمَ دَفْنُ اثْنَيْنِ فَأَكْثَرَ فِي قَبْرٍ إِلَّا لِضَرُورَةٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَأَيُّ قُرْبَةٍ فُعِلَتْ وَجُعِلَ ثَوَابُهَا لِمُسْلِمٍ حَيٍّ أَوْ مَيِّتٍ:</span> نَفَعَهُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) تجصيصه: بناؤه بالجص، وهو ما يبنى به، والجص: بكسر الجيم وفتحها. ينظر: المطلع (ص ١٥٢).<br>(٢) في (ب) و (د): نفعته.</p> </div>